#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: ../help/C/configuring-advanced-options.page:29
msgid ""
"The <cmd>Remove method</cmd> option controls how the file is removed from the file system. File "
"Shredder can rename the file in such a way that it is very hard to detect that it existed. "
"<cmd>Wipesync</cmd> and <cmd>Wipe</cmd> both do this, but <cmd>Wipesync</cmd> makes sure that "
